  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                             </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Reborn the Soul》\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Is a mental illness themed game developed by three people that 。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >presents the symptoms of mental illness in the form of a game。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player plays as a teenager experiencing the pain of mental illness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abstracting the symptoms of mental illness into monsters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player needs to destroy all the monsters in sight,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save your soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New forms can be unlocked after clearing the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can put their favorite equipment in the vault to save.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Here are the features of the game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras/7d3156cf2fa7054b7ae846f19b2b6c3e.avif?t=1744697289\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras_big/7d3156cf2fa7054b7ae846f19b2b6c3e.avif?t=1744697289 width=800 height=452 /></span>Gain psychological knowledge in combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras/321d0a0a4aa4d4c0bb8c52fe419f41a7.avif?t=1744697289\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras_big/321d0a0a4aa4d4c0bb8c52fe419f41a7.avif?t=1744697289 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock mental knowledge and use it in real life！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras/af8ec91c84f46e683eabcdce185b838a.avif?t=1744697289\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras_big/af8ec91c84f46e683eabcdce185b838a.avif?t=1744697289 width=800 height=450 /></span>Feel the pain of mental patients in the story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras/d2edeeb79e7c853572e4497399f7edb4.avif?t=1744697289\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras_big/d2edeeb79e7c853572e4497399f7edb4.avif?t=1744697289 width=800 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat elite monsters and get extra rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras/8ed9aac361e44937bbb3f413ff0f0187.avif?t=1744697289\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras_big/8ed9aac361e44937bbb3f413ff0f0187.avif?t=1744697289 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight two bosses at once until your soul is saved！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras/7f3dd25239a9962d7d0344b63e23e5c8.avif?t=1744697289\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras_big/7f3dd25239a9962d7d0344b63e23e5c8.avif?t=1744697289 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360330/extras/4fbad102e7891be7a44d1905e1e8e688.avif?t=1744697289\" data-big-src=